s-Getty_2.jpg" alt="佐伊·萨尔达娜（Zoe Saldana）" width="1700" height="1166" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/ZoeSaldana-2025-Oscars-Getty_2.jpg 1700w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/ZoeSaldana-2025-Oscars-Getty_2-218x150.jpg 218w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/ZoeSaldana-2025-Oscars-Getty_2-436x300.jpg 436w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/ZoeSaldana-2025-Oscars-Getty_2-400x274.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/ZoeSaldana-2025-Oscars-Getty_2-800x549.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/ZoeSaldana-2025-Oscars-Getty_2-696x477.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/ZoeSaldana-2025-Oscars-Getty_2-1392x955.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/ZoeSaldana-2025-Oscars-Getty_2-1068x733.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 1700px) 100vw, 1700px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3842944" class="wp-caption-text"> Zoe Saldana accepting the Best Actress In A Supporting Role award for &#39;Emilia Pérez&#39; onstage. CREDIT: Kevin Winter/Getty Images</figcaption></figure><p> “And these women are still very universal women that are struggling every day, but trying to survive systemic oppression and trying to find the most authentic voices.</p><p> “So I will stand by that, but I&#39;m also always open to sit down with all of my Mexican brothers and sisters, with love and respect, [to have] a great conversation on how &#39;Emilia Pérez&#39; could have been done better.我欢迎它。”</p><p> During her acceptance speech, she declared herself “a proud child of immigrant parents” and “the first American of Dominican origin to accept an Academy Award”.</p><p> The 97th Academy Awards were hosted by Conan O&#39;Brien for the first time, the comedian taking over duties from Jimmy Kimmel.</p><p> <em>Anora</em> proved the big Oscar winner, taking home five awards including Best Picture, Best Actress for Mikey Madison, Best Director for Sean Baker, Best Original Screenplay and Best Editing.</p><p> <em>The Brutalist</em> followed behind with three, including Best Actor for Adrien Brody, Best Original Score and Best Cinematography, while <em>Dune: Part Two, Wicked</em> and <em>Emilia Perez</em> took two each. See the full list <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/oscars-2025-winners-full-list-3842814">here</a> .</p><p> The post <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/zoe-saldana-apologises-after-being-told-emilia-perez-was-really-hurtful-for-mexicans-3842940">Zoe Saldaña apologises after being told &#39;Emilia Perez&#39; was “really hurtful” for Mexicans</a> appeared first on <a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a> .</p> ;
