论黑人卓越时，我们正在谈论昆西。”</p><p> “Quincy was love, lived out loud in human form.他把这种爱倒入了他人和他的工作中。见到他后，我的生活永远改变了。 He actually discovered me for <em>The Color Purple</em> , which was my first film,” Winfrey said, with Goldberg adding: “Me, too.”</p><blockquote class="twitter-tweet" data-width="550" data-dnt="true"><p lang="en" dir="ltr"> Queen Latifah delivers a beautiful tribute to Quincy Jones with her rendition of &#39;Ease On Down The Road&#39; from <a href="https://twitter.com/hashtag/TheWiz?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">#TheWiz</a> at the <a href="https://twitter.com/hashtag/Oscars?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">#Oscars</a> . <a href="https://t.co/hSWJLLIGxM">pic.twitter.com/hSWJLLIGxM</a></p><p> — Fandango (@Fandango) <a href="https://twitter.com/Fandango/status/1896401786543468584?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">March 3, 2025</a> </p></blockquote><p><script async src="https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><p> “Jones&#39; soundtrack work was particularly impressive given that Black musicians were rarely allowed to work on film and TV projects, and rarer still on those that did not focus on African-American themes,” <a href="https://www.nme.com/features/music-features/quincy-jones-obituary-3809386">wrote <em>NME</em> &#39;s Jordan Bassett in an obituary for Jones</a> .</p><p> “In 2020, he said the renewed energy around the Black Lives Matter movement, which followed the murder of George Floyd, had been “coming a long time, man”, adding: “People have been turning their heads the other way, but it&#39;s all the same to me – misogyny, racism. You have to be taught how to hate somebody.”</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/film-reviews/emilia-perez-review-zoe-saldana-selena-gomez-flawed-musical-melodrama-3805570"><em>Emilia Pérez</em></a> leads this year&#39;s Oscar nominations, followed by <a href="https://www.nme.com/films/the-brutalist"><em>The Brutalist</em></a> , <a href="https://www.nme.com/films/wicked"><em>Wicked</em></a> , <a hre