 by O&#39;Brien for the first time, the comedian taking over duties from Jimmy Kimmel.</p><p> Netflix音乐剧<em>EmiliaPérez</em>是领先的<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/oscars-2025-nominations-full-list-3831350">提名</a>，该音乐剧将获得13个奖项，其中包括最佳影片，而史诗般的戏剧<a href="https://www.nme.com/films/the-brutalist"><em>《野蛮主义者</em></a>》和百老汇适应的<a href="https://www.nme.com/films/wicked"><em>邪恶</em></a>之后，以10项提名。</p><p>其他强大的竞争者包括教皇惊悚<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/film-reviews/conclave-review-pope-ralph-fiennes-stanley-tucci-3815998"><em>片</em></a>和鲍勃·迪伦（Bob Dylan）传记片<a href="https://www.nme.com/films/a-complete-unknown"><em>《完全未知》，</em></a>每个点头八个点头，而喜剧戏剧<a href="https://www.nme.com/films/anora"><em>Anora</em></a>则获得了六项提名。</p><p>今年的仪式将有所变化， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/the-2025-oscars-will-not-include-performances-for-best-original-song-category-3831285">没有最佳原创歌曲的表演</a>，而在<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/entertainment-world-reacts-to-heart-wrenching-los-angeles-wildfires-3827340">最近毁灭性的野火</a>之后，该节目有望纪念洛杉矶。哈里森·福特（Harrison Ford）还因疾病<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/harrison-ford-no-longer-presenting-at-the-2025-oscars-due-to-illness-3842776">而退出了出现</a>。</p><p> The post <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/bob-dylan-reportedly-invited-to-perform-and-present-at-2025-oscars-3842904">Bob Dylan reportedly invited to perform and present at 2025 Oscars</a> appeared first on <a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a> .</p> ;
