>most-watched Halftime Show ever</a> , beating out <a href="https://www.dailymail.co.uk/sport/nfl/article-13080219/usher-halftime-viewed-super-bowl.html" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Usher, who raked in 129.3million viewers</a> , and <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/rihanna-super-bowl-halftime-show-most-watched-3438550">previous title-holder Rihanna for 121million viewers</a> .</p><blockquote class="twitter-tweet" data-width="550" data-dnt="true"><p lang="en" dir="ltr"> <a href="https://twitter.com/hashtag/Oscars?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">#oscars</a>的柯南·奥布莱恩（Conan O&#39;Brien）：“好吧，我们在演出中途进行了一半，这意味着肯德里克·拉马尔（Kendrick Lamar）出来称德雷克为恋童癖了。” <a href="https://t.co/KmbX3QjnlM">pic.twitter.com/kmbx3qjnlm</a></p><p> - 综艺（@Variety） <a href="https://twitter.com/Variety/status/1896383037585363455?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">2025年3月3日</a></p></blockquote><p><script async src="https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><p> Last week, it was reported that <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/drake-has-dropped-key-allegations-from-not-like-us-lawsuit-3840668">Drake has dropped “key allegations” from his lawsuit against Universal Music Group over &#39;Not Like Us&#39;</a> .</p><p> Both Kendrick Lamar and SZA are due to hit the road for a joint tour this year, <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/kendrick-lamar-and-sza-announce-joint-2025-grand-national-north-american-stadium-tour-3818353">performing across North America between April and June</a> . Shortly after their Super Bowl Halftime Show performance, <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/kendrick-lamar-sza-announce-2025-uk-european-stadium-tour-buy-tickets-3836665">the pair announced UK and European stadium tour dates</a> . You can <a href="https://www.ticketmaster.com/kendrick-lamar-tickets/artist/1480454?irgwc=1&amp;clickid=Vkb3RnTcCxyKULZQ3-0DpWWTUkszz025Y1o00M0&amp;camefrom=CFC_BUYAT_2862475&amp;impradid=2862475&amp;REFERRAL_ID=tmfeedbuyat2862475&amp;wt.mc_id=aff_BUYAT_2862475&amp;